## 4) Apollo директива для проверки прав в резолверах

### SDL: директива
```graphql
# schema.graphql (или string в Nest)
directive @auth(
  action: String!
  resource: String!
  resourceIdArg: String
) on FIELD_DEFINITION
```

Идея:
- `action/resource` — константы на схеме
- `resourceIdArg` — имя аргумента резолвера, из которого берем `resourceId`
  - например: `resourceIdArg: "projectId"`

### Реализация директивы (SchemaDirectiveVisitor)
```ts
// src/graphql/directives/auth.directive.ts
import { SchemaDirectiveVisitor } from '@graphql-tools/utils';
import { defaultFieldResolver, GraphQLField } from 'graphql';
import { authDirectiveTransformer } from './auth.directive.transformer'; // опционально
import { Enforcer, Action, ResourceType } from '../../authorization/enforcer';
import { AuthContext } from '../../auth/auth-context';

import {
  ArgumentNode,
  DirectiveNode,
} from 'graphql';
import { ApolloError } from 'apollo-server-errors';

function getStringArg(d: DirectiveNode, name: string): string | undefined {
  return d.arguments?.find(a => a.name.value === name)?.value.kind === 'StringValue'
    ? d.arguments.find(a => a.name.value === name)!.value.value
    : undefined;
}

export class AuthDirective extends SchemaDirectiveVisitor {
  constructor(private enforcer: Enforcer) {
    super();
  }

  visitFieldDefinition(field: GraphQLField<any, any>) {
    const originalResolve = field.resolve ?? defaultFieldResolver;

    field.resolve = async function (source, args, context, info) {
      const directive = info.fieldNodes?.[0]?.directives?.find(
        d => d.name.value === 'auth'
      );

      if (!directive) return originalResolve(source, args, context, info);

      const actionStr = getStringArg(directive, 'action');
      const resourceStr = getStringArg(directive, 'resource');
      const resourceIdArg = getStringArg(directive, 'resourceIdArg');

      if (!actionStr || !resourceStr) {
        throw new ApolloError('Misconfigured @auth directive');
      }

      const authContext = (context as any).authContext as AuthContext | undefined;
      if (!authContext) throw new ApolloError('UNAUTHENTICATED', 'UNAUTHENTICATED');

      const resourceId = resourceIdArg ? args?.[resourceIdArg] : undefined;

      const can = await (this.enforcer as Enforcer).can(
        authContext,
        actionStr as Action,
        resourceStr as ResourceType,
        { resourceId }
      );

      if (!can) {
        // Можно использовать 404 для сокрытия существования
        throw new ApolloError('FORBIDDEN', 'FORBIDDEN');
      }

      return originalResolve(source, args, context, info);
    };

    return field;
  }
}
```

### Подключение директивы в Apollo (Nest)
Используйте `SchemaDirectiveVisitor` через `makeExecutableSchema`/доп. конфиги — зависит от того, как у вас настроен GraphQL модуль. Самый простой путь в Nest: использовать `GraphQLModule` + provider для директивы.

Пример (концептуально):
```ts
// src/graphql/graphql-directives.module.ts
import { Module } from '@nestjs/common';
import { AuthDirective } from './directives/auth.directive';
import { EnforcerImpl } from '../authorization/enforcer-impl';
import { Enforcer } from '../authorization/enforcer';

@Module({
  providers: [
    EnforcerImpl,
